        </div>
        <div class="prodtext">
        	<p>Some chairs are made infrequently and require individual parts to be machined to order.   Peter is seen sanding a chair bend.</p>
        </div>    
    </div>
    <div class="prodright">
        <div class="prodtext">
        	<p>The components are partially assembled, glued and screwed, ready for the addition of weave.   Each type of chair has a different process.   In some the seats are separately made; in some they are part of the main frame, as in the seat Mark is assembling here.   </p>
        </div>    
    	<div class="prodimage">
        	<img src="/images/prod8.jpg" border="0"  height="200" alt="Nails" />
        </div>
    </div>
