		<div class="prodimage">
        	<img src="/images/prod9.jpg" border="0"  height="200" alt="Forming" />        
        </div>
        <div class="prodtext">
        	<p>In some the weave is partially applied at this stage.</p>
        </div>    
    </div>
    <div class="prodright">
        <div class="prodtext">
        	<p>Simon preparing a seat. Each wire is stapled to the seat frame to ensure the product can withstand heavy use.</p>
        </div>    
    	<div class="prodimage">
        	<img src="/images/prod10.jpg" border="0" height="200" alt="Simon" />
