        </div>
        <div class="prodtext">
        	<p>Next comes "upholstery" when the weave is shaped around the frame.  This is a very skilled and tough process, since the fabric has great tensile strength and has to be stretched , shaped and hand-woven over all the tight corners.</p>
<p>Peter upholstering the weave to a frame</p>
        </div>    
    </div>
    <div class="prodright">
        <div class="prodtext">
