        </div>
        <div class="prodtext">
        	<p>Much of the upholstery is done with a back light that illuminates the frame perimeter in the weave to ensure good fixing.</p>
        </div>    
    </div>
    <div class="prodright">
        <div class="prodtext">
        	<p>Once the Chair is completed the weave is sprayed with PVA glue which bonds the strands and stabilizes the shape.   David can be seen spraying a Sereno dining chair</p>
